<font class="print-normal"><P>The new Crimson Talon site is live!&nbsp;&nbsp;Everything has been migrated over, but the old forums will remain active for another week while everyone sets up their new bulletin board account.&nbsp;&nbsp;This change allows the guild to be much more flexible and provide more services:</P><BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px"><P>*Ability for guild members to maintain character profiles.<BR>*Ability to run dozens of guild reports, including keys/flags.<BR>*Ability for guild members to post public/private calendar events.<BR>*Ability for guild members to submit news, stories, and screenshots.<BR>*All this with wysiwyg editors, advanced polling features, and an easy to maintain bulletin board.</P></BLOCKQUOTE><P></P><br />
